In addition, we should build out support for n simultaneous USB mass storage devices, not just one.

370
Wed Jun 25 15:03:04 2014 +0000
Author: Alexandru Timohi <1048135@85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889>
Parent: 5f804079_edd9308f
UUID: e472491f_0b298113
